Christiana Gardikioti:

"I envisioned Mount Parnonas becoming the first 
“Natural Green Factory” of the world and my village Agiannis to become the centre of sustainable development for my country and an example world to be shared and followed by the world. 

The Meraki people Global initiative is all about

1. Inspiring the world to synergize with us in Greece to make productive our mountain again.

2. Respecting its resources, culture and people. 

3. Restoring Greece to its greatness!

MERAKI is the love, skill, perseverance and creativity put in all inspired activities from the smallest task to the biggest accomplishment

Greece is full of these people and I would like to gather them under one roof working TO EXPORT on all 24 villages of Mount Parnonas in Pel/sos Greece 

Re-populating empty Greek Villages with Green and Sustainable businesses/services with Global appeal.Will develop a network of the 24 eco-villages that will experience significant economic growth by promoting eco-food exports, healing products from the herbs, international cultural events with the assistance of a mountain WiFi excellence and innovation centre. 

Our mission: To preserve and share the nature and cultural heritage we were given in mountain Parnonas with the rest of the world by rebuilding Greece to its greatness locally!"
